                    alt="Little Mix"
                />
                
                <h3>Little Mix</h3>
            </div>
        

        
        
    </div>

    
        <p class="teaser">
            The four-piece were formed on the reality TV show &#39;The X Factor&#39; in 2011 and then went on to become the first group to win the series. Following their victory, they signed to Simon Cowell&#39;s record label and have had huge successes ever since, including breaking records previously held by the likes of the Spice Girls as well as selling out world tours.<br />The ladies have had FOUR incredible studio albums with their first, &#39;DNA&#39; released way back in 2012. The group have been killing it ever since!
        </p>
    
    
        <p class="expanded">
            Real Name: Perrie Edwards, Jesy Nelson, Leigh-Anne Pinnock, Jade Thirlwall Born: 10 July 1993 (Perrie), 14 June 1991 (Jesy), 4 October 1991 (Leigh-Anne) and 26 December 1992 (Jade) Height: 5&#39; 3&quot; / 1.63 m (Perrie), 5&#39; 2&quot; / 1.6 m (Jesy), 5&#39; 3&quot; / 1.63 m (Leigh-Anne) and 5&#39; 3&quot; / 1.63 m (Jade) Star Sign: Cancer (Perrie), Gemini (Jesy), Libra (Leigh-Anne) and Capricorn (Jade) Birthplace: South Shields, Tyne and Wear, England (Perrie), Romford, London, England (Jesy), High Wycombe, Buckinghamshire, England (Leigh-Anne) and South Shields, Tyne and Wear, England (Jade).
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="toggle is-hidden" data-action="toggle"
           >
            View more
        </a>
    
</div>

        

    
